# Terraform runtime
**/.terraform/
*.tfplan
plan.json
crash.log

# NEVER ignore .terraform.lock.hcl — it must be committed (provider-versioning.mdc §3)

# State stays remote — except bootstrap/, whose local state is intentionally committed
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup
!bootstrap/*.tfstate

# Local overrides
*.auto.tfvars
override.tf
override.tf.json

.DS_Store
